We, as members, contributors, and leaders, pledge to make participation in our project and community a **harassment-free experience** for everyone, regardless of age, disability, ethnicity, gender identity, level of experience, nationality, personal appearance, race, religion, or sexual identity.

We are committed to fostering an **open, inclusive, and respectful** community.

